Nigeria’s President Muhammadu Buhari Friday approved the reappointment of his Chief of Staff, Abba Kyari and Boss Mustapha as Secretary to the Government of the Federation. “President Muhammadu Buhari has approved the re-appointment of Mr Boss Mustapha as Secretary to the Government of the Federation (SGF), and Malam Abba Kyari as Chief of Staff (COS) to the President,” Buhari’s spokesman, Garba Shehu said. Shehu said both appointments were effective from May 29, 2019. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .